name: r-htssip

owner.description: Bioconda is a distribution of bioinformatics software realized as a channel for the versatile Conda package manager.
owner.name: bioconda

summary: Functions for analyzing high throughput sequencing  stable isotope probing (HTS-SIP) data. Analyses include high resolution stable isotope probing (HR-SIP), multi-window high resolution stable isotope probing (MW-HR-SIP),  and quantitative stable isotope probing (q-SIP).
